.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/161848/', '', 'Glipizide, Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Rosuvastatin, Tolazamide, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Tolbutamide, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belumosudil, More', 1767369485);
